{
  "components": [
    {
      "id": "chat_1",
      "provider": "chat",
      "name": "Chat",
      "config": {
        "hideForm": true,
        "mode": "Source",
        "parameters": {},
        "type": "chat"
      },
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": -10,
          "y": 200
        },
        "nodeType": "default",
        "formDataValid": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "agent_rocketride_1",
      "provider": "agent_rocketride",
      "name": "RocketRide Wave",
      "config": {
        "instructions": [
          "You are DataWhisper, an expert data analyst assistant.",
          "You will be given a SCHEMA, some SAMPLE ROWS, and a QUESTION from the user.",
          "Your ONLY task is to fulfill the user's question with 100% numerical accuracy.",
          "DO NOT COMPUTE ANY NUMBERS YOURSELF. You must use the HTTP tool to execute a plan.",
          "1. Determine the appropriate Pandas operation (e.g., groupby, filter, sort, pct_change) to answer the question.",
          "2. Formulate a JSON plan describing this operation.",
          "3. Call the HTTP tool using a POST request to http://localhost:8000/internal/compute",
          "   The body of the request must be the JSON plan.",
          "4. The API will return a JSON object with this exact contract: { 'value': <string/number/array>, 'operation_used': <string>, 'rows_matched': <integer> }",
          "5. If 'value' is a single number/string, insert it verbatim into your narration. If 'value' is an array or list of multiple rows, DO NOT output the raw JSON array in your narration. Instead, write a natural English sentence like 'Here is the data breakdown:' or summarize the top result.",
          "6. Recommend an appropriate chart type (bar, line, or pie) and the x/y columns.",
          "7. Output ONLY a JSON response in the following exact format (no markdown formatting, no backticks):",
          "   {",
          "     \"answer\": \"<your plain English narration using the verbatim value>\",",
          "     \"numbers\": <the verbatim value from the API>,",
          "     \"columns_used\": [\"<col1>\", \"<col2>\"],",
          "     \"operation\": \"<the operation_used from the API>\",",
          "     \"chart\": { \"type\": \"<bar|line|pie>\", \"x\": \"<col_name>\", \"y\": \"<col_name>\" },",
          "     \"plan\": <your original plan object>",
          "   }"
        ],
        "max_waves": 3,
        "parameters": {}
      },
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 240,
          "y": 200
        },
        "nodeType": "default",
        "formDataValid": true
      },
      "input": [
        {
          "lane": "questions",
          "from": "chat_1"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "response_answers_1",
      "provider": "response_answers",
      "name": "Return Answers",
      "config": {
        "laneName": "answers"
      },
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 470,
          "y": 210
        },
        "nodeType": "default",
        "formDataValid": true
      },
      "input": [
        {
          "lane": "answers",
          "from": "agent_rocketride_1"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "llm_gemini_1",
      "provider": "llm_gemini",
      "name": "Gemini",
      "config": {
        "profile": "gemini-3_1-flash-lite-preview",
        "gemini-3_1-flash-lite-preview": {
          "apikey": "${ROCKETRIDE_GEMINI_KEY}"
        },
        "parameters": {}
      },
      "ui": {
